There have been many famous modern [[circus]]es since the first modern circus was staged by [[Philip Astley]] in [[London]] on January 9, 1768. Many are best known by the name of their principal owner. The following is a list of both circuses and their country of origin. For more information on circuses in general see [[Circus]], or for information regarding the [[Ancient Rome|ancient Roman]] circus, see [[Circus Maximus]].<!--
